  "page": "House Xaq",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold\">House Xaq</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\"><div></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Region</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Koj\" title=\"Koj\">Koj</a> (<a href=\"/index.php/Summer_Isles\" title=\"Summer Isles\">Summer Isles</a>)</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\nPrince of <a href=\"/index.php/Koj\" title=\"Koj\">Koj</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>House Xaq</b> was a noble house from the island of <a href=\"/index.php/Koj\" title=\"Koj\">Koj</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Summer_Isles\" title=\"Summer Isles\">Summer Isles</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Xaq&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Malthar_Xaq\" title=\"Malthar Xaq\">Malthar Xaq</a> was a great shipbuilder and navigator from the <a href=\"/index.php/Summer_Isles\" title=\"Summer Isles\">Summer Isles</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_summer_isles.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_summer_isles.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Historical_members\">Historical members</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Xaq&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Histo